**Detection 6: SOCKS Proxy on Non-Standard Port with SMB Follow-On**

```
title: TheGentlemen Proxy-Chained SMB Enumeration
status: experimental
logsource:
  category: network_connection
detection:
  socks_out:
    DestinationPort|any:
      - 36067
      - 30001
      - 30002
  smb_sweep:
    DestinationPort: 445
  condition: socks_out | near smb_sweep
  # Correlate: external SOCKS connection followed by rapid SMB
  # connection attempts across /24 from the same source within 5 minutes
level: high
```
